8917,0.06159825250506401,0.07870493829250336,0.10427176207304001,-0.011073969304561615,-0.0009555888245813549,0.028893131762742996,0.00582966348156333,0.020360441878437996,-0.030985519289970398,-0.00017037845100276172,0.03756256774067879,0.10189081728458405,0.03626960515975952,0.018481643870472908,0.027105700224637985,-0.008086515590548515,-0.04059796407818794,0.013040771707892418,-0.03224283456802368,-0.05161668732762337,0.022179316729307175,-0.06690005213022232,-0.04799241945147514,-0.06892876327037811,-0.06706617772579193,0.06567979604005814,0.0031706574372947216,0.007834010757505894,-0.0024274508468806744,-0.07585257291793823,-0.05041328817605972,0.021040361374616623,-0.04113034904003143,-0.09213363379240036,-0.03539528697729111,0.10603941231966019,-0.01768483966588974,0.06115587428212166,-0.012731806375086308],"timestamp":"2026-02-23T02:57:52.436Z","quality":1},{"id":"mem-4c348898-1771823238468","query":"How long can I be overseas before my Age Pension is affected?","answer":"If you are receiving the Age Pension and plan to travel overseas, you need to be aware of the following rules regarding how long you can be away before your pension is affected:\n\n1. **Duration of Stay**: You can be outside Australia for up to 6 weeks without affecting your Age Pension. If you are away for more than 6 weeks, you must inform Services Australia.\n\n2. **Permanent or Long-Term Move**: If you are going to live in another country or will be away for an extended period, your Age Pension may be impacted, and you must notify Services Australia.\n\n3. **Reporting Requirements**: You must tell Services Australia if you are leaving Australia and any of the following apply:\n   - You are going to live in another country.\n   - You will be away for more than 6 weeks.\n   - You are receiving Age Pension under a social security agreement with another country.\n   - You are leaving Australia within 2 years after coming back to live and started receiving Age Pension since then.\n\n4. **Payment Adjustments**: If you are outside Australia for an extended period, your pension may be paid differently, and you must continue to meet the qualification rules at all times [Source 2][Source 3][Source 7].\n\nMake sure to keep Services Australia informed about your travel plans to ensure you receive the correct payment while you are away.","sources":[{"index":1,"file":"general/residence-rules-for-age-pension.md","url":"https://www.servicesaustralia.gov.au/residence-rules-for-age-pension","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.3804269357976662},{"index":2,"file":"pensions/when-and-how-to-tell-us-about-overseas-travel-if-you-get-age-pension.md","url":"https://www.servicesaustralia.gov.au/when-and-how-to-tell-us-about-overseas-travel-if-you-get-age-pension","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.38588044420504725},{"index":3,"file":"pensions/travel-outside-australia-rules-for-age-pension.md","url":"https://www.servicesaustralia.gov.au/travel-outside-australia-rules-for-age-pension","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.40025154333383517},{"index":4,"file":"general/prepare-to-transfer-to-age-pension-if-you-get-disability-support-pension.md","url":"https://www.servicesaustralia.gov.au/prepare-to-transfer-to-age-pension-if-you-get-disability-support-pension","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.4080199629831518},{"index":5,"file":"general/how-to-prepare-to-claim-age-pension.md","url":"https://www.servicesaustralia.gov.au/how-to-prepare-to-claim-age-pension","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.417188980569854},{"index":6,"file":"pensions/travel-outside-australia-rules-for-pension-supplement.md","url":"https://www.servicesaustralia.gov.au/travel-outside-australia-rules-for-pension-supplement","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.41953928065575374},{"index":7,"file":"pensions/when-and-how-to-tell-us-about-overseas-travel-if-you-get-age-pension.md","url":"https://www.servicesaustralia.gov.au/when-and-how-to-tell-us-about-overseas-travel-if-you-get-age-pension","pageStart":1,"pageE